This function is used to find the position of the first occurrence of a substring in a string.
Example:
strpos("emily", "e");   // 0
strpos("emily", "i");   // 2
strpos("emily", "ily"); // 2
strpos("emily", "zxc"); // false

Another example:
if (strpos("david","h") === false) {
  print "Sorry, no 'h' in 'david'";
}
// prints the "Sorry...." message

